history.content:
SCET Kaggle competition is now live!

It is not too late to join SCET Innovation Fellows Program. All Berkeley students are eligible to join to start challenges and collect points at any time!

SCET Innovation Fellows Kaggle Competition in partnership with Berkeley Disaster Lab 

WHO should compete: anyone interested in ML or natural disaster response or innovation 

WHEN: now until Mar. 28 

WHY: (1) earn points toward SCET Innovation Fellows Certificate (2) opportunity to be selected for Berkeley Disaster X-Lab Innovation Challenge (3) build project portfolio

RESOURCES: https://www.kaggle.com/learn

https://www.kaggle.com/c/scet
